    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a reliable daily driver or a rewarding project for an enthusiast. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some routine suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly entry into this model.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The engine and transmission are reliable, and the car has received regular maintenance. The exterior and interior show minor signs of wear and cosmetic imperfections consistent with its age.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
