    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning motorist. It exhibits a commendable balance of mechanical precision and aesthetic preservation, reflecting a history of diligent care. Engineered for sustained performance, the drivetrain remains robust, while the interior and exterior appointments maintain a sophisticated presentation. This offering provides a superior value proposition for those seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this well-appointed example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and I honestly think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "For sale is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), a refined driver\u2019s specimen featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This rear-wheel-drive icon is paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, offering precise shift gates and mechanical engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The suspension retains its factory composure with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing exceptional lateral grip. The exterior exhibits a clean finish with minor road wear, while the interior shows light patina on the leather bolsters. Mechanically robust and free of bore scoring symptoms, this 911 is an ideal entry for the purist seeking a balanced, high-revving flat-six experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy luster, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of careful road use. The interior is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since new. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a cooling system flush. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and stable ride. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts. This is a reliable, honest example of a well-loved car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical excellence and roadworthiness. While showing signs of respectful prior ownership, its structural integrity and drivetrain remain in superior condition, offering a sophisticated driving experience. This is a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a high-caliber vehicle at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great and drives even better? This beauty has been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is ready for its next adventure. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car won\u2019t let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This engine remains a masterpiece of engineering, delivering 414 hp with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a 6-speed manual transmission with precise synchro engagement and a factory variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its structural integrity with a firm EDC (Electronic Damper Control) suspension system and communicative hydraulic steering. Minor cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance.",
